snippet.title: LandRocker Pro is Coming! | Gameplay Demo April 2024
snippet.description:
About LandRocker
LandRocker is a P2E game about discovery and space exploration. As a brave and resourceful player, you'll journey to faraway planets, launching exhilarating mining missions to collect rare and valuable resources such as NFTs, crypto tokens, and crafting materials. 

Learn more:
Play: https://landrocker.io/start-mining
Website: https://landrocker.io/
Telegram: https://t.me/landrockerchat
Twitter: https://twitter.com/landrocker_io
Medium: https://landrocker.medium.com/
Discord: https://discord.gg/landrocker
All links: https://side.xyz/landrocker
